ComicInfo.Title: Assault on Olympia!
ComicInfo.Summary: Assault on Olympia!: Thor travels to Olympus with the other Eternals. While there, The Forgotten One is sent by the Celestials to warn the Eternals to not interfere with the 50 year judgement of the Earth.
